1
00:02:03,223 --> 00:02:04,986
Give up. Give up, I said.

2
00:02:06,693 --> 00:02:07,990
Get out of my face.

3
00:02:11,998 --> 00:02:13,693
Move it. Move it.

4
00:02:15,135 --> 00:02:16,466
Fuck you up!

5
00:02:21,141 --> 00:02:22,802
Break it up!

6
00:02:41,561 --> 00:02:43,324
Come on, back off.
Take your hands off me.

7
00:03:00,580 --> 00:03:01,672
Take this, take this!

8
00:03:21,267 --> 00:03:23,064
Tell me, Twitch.

9
00:03:24,070 --> 00:03:26,095
-Who started this?
-My name's Twitch...

10
00:03:26,306 --> 00:03:29,833
...and I ain't no snitch.
I don't know nothing, man.

11
00:03:30,510 --> 00:03:32,171
You're worried?

12
00:03:32,745 --> 00:03:34,542
About them?

13
00:03:35,982 --> 00:03:38,212
What they could do to you?

14
00:03:39,052 --> 00:03:41,145
You should worry more about me.

15
00:03:41,354 --> 00:03:45,017
-And what I'm gonna do to you.
-Look, man, I'm just working.

16
00:03:45,225 --> 00:03:47,090
Just doing my time.

17
00:03:47,293 --> 00:03:49,420
Just doing my time.

18
00:03:51,064 --> 00:03:53,498
Model citizen.

19
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:57,301
See, Twitch has been here
a long time...

20
00:03:57,503 --> 00:03:59,664
...seen lot of shit go down.

21
00:03:59,872 --> 00:04:03,069
Like inmates trying to take over.

22
00:04:03,276 --> 00:04:06,939
But I slapped them down
like little bitches.

23
00:04:07,146 --> 00:04:10,240
Nobody wins in my island...

24
00:04:10,450 --> 00:04:11,747
...but me.

25
00:04:14,487 --> 00:04:17,217
What do you think, homeys?

26
00:04:17,423 --> 00:04:20,790
Should I put any of you in the hole?

27
00:04:20,994 --> 00:04:22,825
Shit.

28
00:04:23,029 --> 00:04:25,862
Lot of guys like you in the hole...

29
00:04:26,065 --> 00:04:28,659
...guys who think they're tough...

30
00:04:29,502 --> 00:04:32,903
...guys who are beginning
to believe...

31
00:04:33,106 --> 00:04:35,734
...they're bigger...

32
00:04:35,942 --> 00:04:38,137
...than my island.

33
00:04:44,117 --> 00:04:46,347
You bay beauties...

34
00:04:46,552 --> 00:04:49,988
...you don't know
how fucking good you got it.

35
00:04:50,189 --> 00:04:51,656
Hey...

36
00:04:51,858 --> 00:04:53,553
...bag of bones.

37
00:04:54,227 --> 00:04:57,663
You wouldn't last two weeks
in a place like Creighton.

38
00:04:57,864 --> 00:04:59,661
-Toughest max-security joint...
-Creigh--?

39
00:04:59,866 --> 00:05:01,800
...in the country.

40
00:05:02,368 --> 00:05:04,632
In case you never heard of it.

41
00:05:05,571 --> 00:05:07,869
It's where society took a shit.

42
00:05:08,074 --> 00:05:11,475
And built a 40-foot wall around it.

43
00:05:11,678 --> 00:05:15,341
And any of you could end up there...

44
00:05:15,548 --> 00:05:18,540
...with a snap of my fingers.

45
00:05:19,452 --> 00:05:21,249
So...

46
00:05:21,454 --> 00:05:24,389
...everybody's on notice.

47
00:05:24,590 --> 00:05:27,388
Whoever starts the next fight...

48
00:05:28,194 --> 00:05:33,063
...gets a free ride, no questions asked,
to Creighton.

49
00:05:33,266 --> 00:05:38,966
Then you can see
how bad you really are.

50
00:05:40,506 --> 00:05:42,531
Now, get them back to their cages.

51
00:05:42,742 --> 00:05:45,006
They're starting to give me
indigestion.

52
00:05:49,082 --> 00:05:51,448
Come on, line it up and let's move.

53
00:05:52,819 --> 00:05:55,117
Lock your chains. Let's go.

54
00:05:55,321 --> 00:05:58,290
-That means you too.
-Back it up.

55
00:05:58,491 --> 00:06:00,516
Creighton, huh?
That's in Missouri, ain't it?

56
00:06:16,676 --> 00:06:18,268
Hey, Twitch.

57
00:06:18,478 --> 00:06:20,708
Heard you got deep-sixed
at your parole hearing.

58
00:06:20,913 --> 00:06:23,905
Looks like you're not getting out
anytime soon.

59
00:06:24,117 --> 00:06:26,415
Oh, fuck you, Hubert.

60
00:06:26,619 --> 00:06:29,952
I'm out in a month.
Mark it on your calendar.

61
00:06:30,156 --> 00:06:32,624
While you rot in here, I get the gold.

62
00:06:32,825 --> 00:06:34,952
Yeah, I'll be out a lot sooner
than you think.

63
00:06:35,161 --> 00:06:37,755
Oh, yeah? You gonna dog paddle
off this rock?

64
00:06:37,964 --> 00:06:42,060
-Oh, I got ways.
-A month, Twitch. That's what I got.

65
00:06:42,268 --> 00:06:45,237
Yeah? And I got a nice,
stern ass-whupping for you...

66
00:06:45,438 --> 00:06:48,236
...if you don't leave me
the fuck alone.

67
00:06:55,581 --> 00:06:57,139
You.

68
00:06:57,583 --> 00:06:59,380
You're gonna move, man?
Wanna move a play?

69
00:06:59,585 --> 00:07:00,847
No.

70
00:07:01,888 --> 00:07:03,185
Shit.

71
00:07:03,389 --> 00:07:05,516
Perfect.

72
00:07:06,559 --> 00:07:09,392
Hey. What's up, motherfucker?

73
00:07:09,595 --> 00:07:12,564
-I'm talking to you, motherfucker.
-What do you want, Twitch?

74
00:07:12,765 --> 00:07:14,790
I wanna kick your ass.

75
00:07:15,001 --> 00:07:18,164
-Man, come on, get your ass up.
-You can't be serious.

76
00:07:18,371 --> 00:07:20,771
Nigga, you've been talking shit
about me.

77
00:07:20,973 --> 00:07:22,133
When? What proof you got?

78
00:07:22,341 --> 00:07:25,174
I don't need no proof.
Man, you sound like a lawyer.

79
00:07:25,378 --> 00:07:27,539
How can you see with these
motherfuckers on here--

80
00:07:27,747 --> 00:07:29,738
-Give them back.
-Fuck, no.

81
00:07:29,949 --> 00:07:33,680
Why don't you come get them from me
so I could kick your ass?

82
00:07:33,886 --> 00:07:35,217
You know I'm out in a month.

83
00:07:35,421 --> 00:07:37,651
-I'm not gonna fight you.
-Damn.

84
00:07:39,358 --> 00:07:42,418
-But my bitch will.
-What bitch?

85
00:07:44,096 --> 00:07:47,031
Oh, shit. Okay.
Here. Hey, you gotta--

86
00:07:52,738 --> 00:07:54,262
Come here.

87
00:07:54,841 --> 00:07:56,468
-Fuck, yeah.
-Oh, shit.

88
00:08:08,154 --> 00:08:10,179
Get up and walk.
Get up and walk.

89
00:08:10,389 --> 00:08:12,721
-What was that?
-Easy, easy.

90
00:08:12,925 --> 00:08:14,722
-Get up.
-I'll kick your ass.

91
00:08:14,927 --> 00:08:18,158
You make sure you tell the warden
that I started this, you hear me?

92
00:08:18,364 --> 00:08:21,663
You hear me? You tell-- What the fuck
are you--? I'll kick your ass too.

93
00:08:46,559 --> 00:08:49,892
Good morning, gentlemen.
Welcome to Creighton.

94
00:08:51,330 --> 00:08:55,164
My name is Mr. Wallace,
and I'm the warden of this prison.

95
00:08:55,368 --> 00:08:58,428
I wanted to personally greet you
by saying:

96
00:08:58,638 --> 00:09:00,765
I run a tight ship.

97
00:09:00,973 --> 00:09:03,840
My prison, my rules.

98
00:09:04,443 --> 00:09:08,709
Best advice I can give to you
is keep to yourself...

99
00:09:08,915 --> 00:09:11,816
...do your time
and don't break my rules.

100
00:09:12,018 --> 00:09:13,781
No matter how tough
you think you are--

101
00:09:13,986 --> 00:09:16,819
And I know some of you think
you're real tough.

102
00:09:17,690 --> 00:09:19,749
--I will break you.

103
00:09:20,192 --> 00:09:21,989
That's a promise.

104
00:09:22,194 --> 00:09:23,991
Understood?

105
00:09:24,196 --> 00:09:27,222
I got your back. I'm with you.

106
00:09:33,306 --> 00:09:34,466
Step forward.

107
00:09:38,644 --> 00:09:40,771
Listen up, punk.

108
00:09:40,980 --> 00:09:45,644
I know you like to cause problems.
That's why you got sent here.

109
00:09:45,851 --> 00:09:50,982
I'm gonna personally see to it
that that doesn't happen anymore.

110
00:09:51,190 --> 00:09:55,559
My officers will resort
to any and all measures necessary...

111
00:09:55,761 --> 00:09:57,592
...to keep you in line.

112
00:09:57,797 --> 00:09:59,560
Understand?

113
00:10:00,132 --> 00:10:01,895
Whatever you say, man. I'm not--

114
00:10:02,101 --> 00:10:03,796
You'll keep your nose clean...

115
00:10:04,003 --> 00:10:07,268
...and stay out of other people's
affairs, won't you?

116
00:10:07,807 --> 00:10:11,106
Hey, man, look. You know,
I only concentrate on my own--

117
00:10:13,646 --> 00:10:17,082
I'm not sure
I really heard you correctly.

118
00:10:17,283 --> 00:10:20,446
I just want to do my time and leave.

119
00:10:20,653 --> 00:10:22,951
That's what I thought you said.

120
00:10:24,023 --> 00:10:26,150
I'll remember you.

121
00:10:34,233 --> 00:10:38,260
Pick up your prison blues
and your shoes.

122
00:10:38,471 --> 00:10:40,564
Show them to their cellblocks.

123
00:10:41,073 --> 00:10:43,234
-Here you go.
-Next.

124
00:10:43,442 --> 00:10:46,206
-Here you go.
-Next.

125
00:10:46,679 --> 00:10:47,646
Here you go.

126
00:10:47,847 --> 00:10:50,509
Where you got your soap, kid?

127
00:10:50,716 --> 00:10:54,243
Shake my hand.
Come on. Shake my hand.

128
00:11:12,605 --> 00:11:14,072
This shit they call food--

129
00:11:14,273 --> 00:11:15,706
Keep your eyes on the room.

130
00:11:15,908 --> 00:11:19,036
-Copy that.
-Anything could be a diversion.

131
00:11:23,082 --> 00:11:27,041
Only take one second for these
bastards to start killing each other.

132
00:11:27,753 --> 00:11:31,018
Sometimes I wonder why we bother
standing in the way.

133
00:11:41,267 --> 00:11:43,861
How long I gotta wait
in line to get food?

134
00:12:21,540 --> 00:12:22,768
What's up with that?

135
00:12:22,975 --> 00:12:26,240
<i>Baboso wants more money
for bringing in the piece.</i>

136
00:12:26,445 --> 00:12:28,777
<i>Mira, you know
how much that mule was paid?</i>

137
00:12:28,981 --> 00:12:30,915
Let me just cut him a piece.

138
00:12:36,856 --> 00:12:38,983
What if this motherfucker's
double-dealing...

139
00:12:39,191 --> 00:12:40,590
...with the Disciples, homes?

140
00:12:40,793 --> 00:12:43,421
-Let me do this.
-Are you sure?

141
00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:05,811
You shouldn't be sitting here,
brother.

142
00:13:06,886 --> 00:13:08,148
Is that right?

143
00:13:08,354 --> 00:13:11,152
Just trying to give you
some friendly advice.

144
00:13:11,357 --> 00:13:13,325
Come with me
or take your chances with them.

145
00:13:16,996 --> 00:13:19,863
-So I should come with you, huh?
-Yeah.

146
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:24,231
-And not with them?
-Unless you got a loco death wish.

147
00:13:24,436 --> 00:13:28,634
And what if I just wanna
kick it here, keep to myself?

148
00:13:28,841 --> 00:13:31,469
Then I'd imagine
you'd get two shanks in you.

149
00:13:31,677 --> 00:13:33,110
One from each side.

150
00:13:41,353 --> 00:13:43,787
I don't see no shanks in him.

151
00:13:43,989 --> 00:13:47,152
Burke? Don't go near him.

152
00:13:48,027 --> 00:13:50,518
-Why?
-Because he don't want you to.

153
00:13:50,729 --> 00:13:51,787
How you know?

154
00:13:51,997 --> 00:13:55,125
Burke don't give a fuck about
anybody in here but himseIf.

155
00:13:55,901 --> 00:13:57,425
And that's cool for him.

156
00:13:57,636 --> 00:13:59,797
He can fight his own fights.

157
00:14:00,439 --> 00:14:02,031
But you....

158
00:14:02,875 --> 00:14:05,400
...you wouldn't last a heartbeat.

159
00:14:05,611 --> 00:14:08,478
Come on, I think you gonna
need some friends.

160
00:14:08,981 --> 00:14:11,142
Man, you see these?
I don't need shit.

161
00:14:11,450 --> 00:14:14,715
Put that little motherfucker away.
Let's go see Angel.

162
00:14:24,797 --> 00:14:27,595
Good to meet you.
Name's Angel.

163
00:14:27,800 --> 00:14:29,700
My name's Twitch. What's up?

164
00:14:30,035 --> 00:14:32,026
Right on. Shit.

165
00:14:32,238 --> 00:14:35,366
I'm from L.A. You know, it's a small
little city. You ever heard of it?

166
00:14:35,574 --> 00:14:36,905
I got people in L.A.

167
00:14:37,109 --> 00:14:38,838
I don't.

168
00:14:39,044 --> 00:14:41,035
You a long way from the ocean.

169
00:14:41,247 --> 00:14:43,238
This ain't Malibu.

170
00:14:43,449 --> 00:14:46,509
Every cell is the same to me, man.
Shit, you know--

171
00:14:46,719 --> 00:14:49,552
Ain't the cells
you got to worry about.

172
00:14:50,055 --> 00:14:52,751
-You know who I am?
-Not really, am I su--

173
00:14:52,958 --> 00:14:55,119
Wallace tell you nothing about me
when you got here?

174
00:14:55,327 --> 00:14:56,794
Wallace?

175
00:14:56,996 --> 00:14:58,054
That's the warden, right?

176
00:14:58,664 --> 00:15:00,461
Yeah, he like to think so...

177
00:15:00,666 --> 00:15:03,396
...running around here
giving orders with his hard ass.

178
00:15:03,602 --> 00:15:05,593
But in reality...

179
00:15:06,338 --> 00:15:08,203
...I'm the nigga in charge.

180
00:15:09,108 --> 00:15:12,339
I got what you call arrangements.

181
00:15:12,978 --> 00:15:14,707
So you have any problems...

182
00:15:15,147 --> 00:15:17,479
...or need any favors...

183
00:15:17,950 --> 00:15:19,383
...you come see me.

184
00:15:20,185 --> 00:15:21,743
And all I ask in return...

185
00:15:23,088 --> 00:15:26,421
-...is your loyalty.
-Sounds good to me, you know.

186
00:15:26,625 --> 00:15:28,820
-I only--
-You got to wear the mark.

187
00:15:29,028 --> 00:15:30,552
Mark?

188
00:15:35,534 --> 00:15:37,468
Angel of Death.

189
00:15:37,803 --> 00:15:39,430
That's what binds us.

190
00:15:39,638 --> 00:15:41,902
Damn. Y'all ain't got
no other type of membership?

191
00:15:42,107 --> 00:15:44,041
You know, like cards or some shit?

192
00:15:44,243 --> 00:15:45,972
Are you in, brother?

193
00:15:46,178 --> 00:15:50,171
Man, I only been here for a day.
Y'all don't even know me.

194
00:15:50,382 --> 00:15:52,043
How you know
I wanna roll with y'all?

195
00:15:52,251 --> 00:15:53,582
Is that a threat?I

196
00:15:56,255 --> 00:15:58,951
-Look, man, I'm just saying, man--
-Either you with us...

197
00:15:59,158 --> 00:16:00,921
...or you with Cortez.

198
00:16:01,126 --> 00:16:03,924
-I ain't with nobody.
-Listen, brother.

199
00:16:04,129 --> 00:16:05,460
There's a war coming on.

200
00:16:05,664 --> 00:16:08,326
You wear this mark, I guarantee
you won't be a casualty.

201
00:16:11,236 --> 00:16:12,999
Come on.

202
00:16:15,307 --> 00:16:16,501
Move it.

203
00:16:16,709 --> 00:16:20,110
I say we get the brothers together,
man, and make this happen.

204
00:16:20,312 --> 00:16:22,337
-Get up in the line now.
-Get out of my way.

205
00:16:22,548 --> 00:16:25,779
It's just a matter of time before shit
hits the fan with Cortez and his gang.

206
00:16:25,985 --> 00:16:27,316
Be cool, baby, we'll get him.

207
00:16:27,519 --> 00:16:29,487
These motherfuckers.
What are we waiting on?

208
00:16:29,688 --> 00:16:32,156
-We will. We will.
-Come on, when?

209
00:16:32,358 --> 00:16:35,088
When the fuck I say so.

210
00:16:35,294 --> 00:16:39,094
You think you could run this shit
better than me, huh?

211
00:16:39,932 --> 00:16:41,661
Look. What I'm saying is...

212
00:16:41,867 --> 00:16:44,097
...Cortez is bringing in more guards
and more money...

213
00:16:44,303 --> 00:16:46,464
...while you sit around
waiting on God to give you...

214
00:16:46,672 --> 00:16:48,572
-...a motherfucking message.
-Let me ask you--

215
00:16:48,774 --> 00:16:50,469
What the fuck was that?

216
00:16:51,844 --> 00:16:53,835
You were in my way.

217
00:16:55,414 --> 00:16:57,279
You know something, Burke?

218
00:16:57,483 --> 00:17:00,975
It's about time you fucking learn
how things operate around here.

219
00:17:01,186 --> 00:17:02,710
And you're gonna show me?

220
00:17:02,921 --> 00:17:06,914
Yeah. Go ahead.
I'll let you take the first swing.

221
00:17:07,559 --> 00:17:10,426
Fuck up some of that good behavior
you got going.

222
00:17:10,629 --> 00:17:13,564
-Another time, Angel.
-Don't you walk away from me, Burke.

223
00:17:13,766 --> 00:17:16,564
Don't you fucking walk away
from me, Burke!

224
00:17:16,769 --> 00:17:21,331
One day. You be ready, Burke.
One day.

225
00:17:21,540 --> 00:17:23,371
Dirt nap.

226
00:17:23,575 --> 00:17:25,440
Come on.

227
00:17:42,594 --> 00:17:44,528
We have a deal, right?

228
00:17:45,998 --> 00:17:47,556
Right?

229
00:17:49,201 --> 00:17:51,294
We got the deal.

230
00:17:54,940 --> 00:17:56,567
Okay.

231
00:18:45,324 --> 00:18:47,224
So you Burke, huh?

232
00:18:47,759 --> 00:18:49,522
Ain't that your name?

233
00:18:57,302 --> 00:19:00,794
You know, I heard that you don't
deal with none of the gangs and....

234
00:19:01,006 --> 00:19:02,701
You don't fool with none of that, huh?

235
00:19:02,908 --> 00:19:05,468
Angel's scared of you.

236
00:19:05,677 --> 00:19:09,204
Cortez is afraid of you.

237
00:19:09,414 --> 00:19:11,644
They afraid of me too, you know.

238
00:19:11,850 --> 00:19:14,375
You know, I don't play too much, man.

239
00:19:16,421 --> 00:19:18,116
You a loner, huh?

240
00:19:18,323 --> 00:19:20,052
I'm a loner too,
you know what I'm saying.

241
00:19:20,259 --> 00:19:23,194
Ain't too much I do, you know.
I don't really, you know, get involved--

242
00:19:23,395 --> 00:19:26,159
Shut up and keep it that way.

243
00:19:29,434 --> 00:19:33,131
-I'm only trying to make it a little easier.
-Don't.

244
00:19:38,610 --> 00:19:41,443
So what you in for anyway, man?
What, you killed somebody?

245
00:19:41,647 --> 00:19:44,013
What, you robbed a bank
or something?

246
00:19:44,216 --> 00:19:46,776
I was thinking about doing
something like that myself, man.

247
00:19:46,985 --> 00:19:51,046
-You could tell me. l'm your boy, man.
-Shut up, will you?

248
00:19:51,256 --> 00:19:53,315
Damn.

249
00:19:53,525 --> 00:19:55,925
Whatever. Shit.

250
00:19:59,464 --> 00:20:03,127
You know, if you don't wanna talk
