Hey, Burke. Hold on, man.

820
01:02:38,528 --> 01:02:40,928
Wallace, is the governor on his way?

821
01:02:41,731 --> 01:02:43,824
<i>What do you want with him?</i>

822
01:02:53,309 --> 01:02:56,073
This is the governor. I'm on my way.
