under control.

830
01:03:15,531 --> 01:03:17,795
I'll be there as soon as I can.

831
01:03:21,904 --> 01:03:24,771
Wait, wait. Hold on, Burke.

832
01:03:24,974 --> 01:03:27,135
-Hold on. Damn.
-Shit.

833
01:03:27,343 --> 01:03:30,210
-Come on, give me a hand.
-Wait, wait, wait. Let me try this.

834
01:03:30,413 --> 01:03:31,846
Pull.

835
01:03:32,048 --> 01:03:34,039
<i>-Just....
-Over here, hermano.</i>

836
01:03:34,917 --> 01:03:36,646
Come on.

837
01:03:36,853 --> 01:03:38,946
-Come on.
-I can't.

838
01:03:39,155 --> 01:03:42,181
-Wait. I got an idea, I got an idea.
