but I didn't.

851
01:04:22,598 --> 01:04:24,862
Cops found him at my house
with a bag full of cash.

852
01:04:25,101 --> 01:04:27,194
-Bag full of cash?
-Yeah.

853
01:04:27,403 --> 01:04:31,567
He implicated me, knocked
a couple of years off his sentence.

854
01:04:32,542 --> 01:04:34,976
I got five years.

855
01:04:35,511 --> 01:04:37,240
I lost my wife.

856
01:04:37,447 --> 01:04:40,348
