was in the conjugal room.

882
01:06:40,369 --> 01:06:43,861
All right, let's get in there.
I wanna talk to this Cortez.

883
01:06:52,949 --> 01:06:54,678
Burke locked us up.
He's a dead man.

884
01:06:54,884 --> 01:06:59,048
Hey, you do this thing,
you're gonna get out of here. Soon.

885
01:06:59,255 --> 01:07:00,779
Got it?

886
01:07:04,193 --> 01:07:06,991
This place is falling apart, man.

887
01:07:07,363 --> 01:07:10,821
-Oh, shit.
-Burke, I've been looking for you.

888
01:07:11,400 --> 01:07:12,765
Check it out, man.

889
01:07:12,969 --> 01:07:13,936
Where's Cortez?

890
01:07:14,136 --> 01:07:17,071
You just follow me. I know
where that motherfucker Cortez is, bro.

891
01:07:17,273 --> 01:07:18,763
