Justice Jane McPherson...</i>

929
01:11:14,777 --> 01:11:16,574
<i>...just landed at New Alcatraz.</i>

930
01:11:16,779 --> 01:11:19,839
<i>She's here to witness
the execution of Lester McKenna.</i>

931
01:11:20,049 --> 01:11:23,075
