for a shitload of cash, you understand?

933
01:11:26,422 --> 01:11:27,582
Gold bricks.

934
01:11:28,057 --> 01:11:30,150
<i>McPherson is the judge
who sentenced McKenna...</i>

935
01:11:30,359 --> 01:11:34,819
