1012
01:16:04,299 --> 01:16:07,029
-...and I'll cut you in.
-Don't play me.

1013
01:16:07,236 --> 01:16:08,396
I'm not trying to play you.

1014
01:16:08,604 --> 01:16:11,437
I'll tell you where it is,
I'll draw you a map. Come on, man.

1015
01:16:11,640 --> 01:16:12,971
You're an inmate.

1016
01:16:13,175 --> 01:16:15,643
