get the fuck out of my way.

1020
01:16:27,122 --> 01:16:30,990
-I can't let you do that, Cortez.
-Oh, you can and you will.

1021
01:16:32,194 --> 01:16:33,889
Dad! Dad!

1022
01:16:35,364 --> 01:16:37,730
