1023
01:16:47,042 --> 01:16:48,009
Move!

1024
01:16:54,116 --> 01:16:56,641
Go, go, go.

1025
01:17:11,767 --> 01:17:13,667
Move.

1026
01:17:31,820 --> 01:17:33,981
-Cortez!
-Dad! Dad!

1027
01:17:34,189 --> 01:17:35,315
Shut up!

1028
01:18:29,311 --> 01:18:30,369
Dad!

1029
01:18:47,729 --> 01:18:49,890
Sorry about your dad.

1030
01:18:55,170 --> 01:18:57,365
You ain't going nowhere, fool.

1031
01:18:57,573 --> 01:18:59,837
-Fucker, get out of my way.
-Get your ass in there.

1032
01:19:00,042 --> 01:19:01,031
-Fuck.
-Get your ass in--

1033
01:19:01,243 --> 01:19:02,210
What?

1034
01:19:02,411 --> 01:19:04,208
