through windows?

1035
01:19:04,413 --> 01:19:07,746
-Get your ass that way. Go.
-Fuck.

1036
01:19:07,950 --> 01:19:09,417
I should pop you right now.

1037
01:19:09,618 --> 01:19:12,951
No, I should whoop your ass first,
then pop it.

1038
01:19:13,155 --> 01:19:14,247
Bernard.

1039
01:19:58,800 --> 01:20:00,927
Dad, stop. You're gonna kill him.

1040
01:20:01,870 --> 01:20:03,360
Dad.

1041
01:20:06,174 --> 01:20:08,142
-Are you okay, baby?
-Yeah.

1042
01:20:08,510 --> 01:20:10,535
-Let's go, let's go.
-Come on.

1043
01:20:11,413 --> 01:20:14,905
-You all right, man?
-I'm alive, dude.

1044
01:20:15,117 --> 01:20:18,052
Eric, you guys get Cortez inside
right now.

1045
01:20:24,393 --> 01:20:25,360
Everything okay?

1046
01:20:27,963 --> 01:20:31,831
