for Christmas?

1136
01:25:23,725 --> 01:25:26,819
-Bernard.
-You guys don't have to do that, now.

1137
01:25:27,028 --> 01:25:28,086
Oh, that's not far at all.

1138
01:25:28,296 --> 01:25:30,355
Missouri is a hop,
skip and a jump away...

1139
01:25:30,565 --> 01:25:32,465
...when you're in first class.

1140
01:25:32,667 --> 01:25:35,932
Now, you know we supposed
to go see Mama for Christmas.

1141
01:25:36,137 --> 01:25:39,834
Like I said, it sounds like a great idea
to come here for Christmas.

1142
01:25:40,041 --> 01:25:42,032
Oh, don't you disrespect
my mama like that.

1143
01:25:42,243 --> 01:25:46,543
I said we gonna take his daughter here
to see him, that's what we're gonna do.

1144
01:25:46,748 --> 01:25:48,773
No, we not.
Not on no Christmas, we ain't.

1145
01:25:48,984 --> 01:25:51,077
I don't know who you think you are.
Stop calling--

1146
01:25:51,286 --> 01:25:53,618
How many times I gotta tell you
to stop calling me ''woman''?

1147
01:25:53,822 --> 01:25:55,187
-You all high and mighty.
-What's your problem?

1148
01:25:55,390 --> 01:25:57,381
You ain't got no bling like me.
You been trouble.

1149
01:25:57,592 --> 01:25:59,719
-You should've never called me.
-I should've never called.

1150
01:25:59,928 --> 01:26:01,520
Ever since you put on this little hat--

1151
01:26:01,730 --> 01:26:02,924
-Anyway, Burke.
-We're going--

1152
01:26:03,131 --> 01:26:05,065
You don't talk to me like that.

1153
01:26:05,266 --> 01:26:07,860
Man, I don't wanna talk to you.
You ain't got no say in this.

1154
01:26:08,069 --> 01:26:10,537
-I know--
-Whatever. Whatever.

